// FIXED: Require OAuth routes/strategies (assume/create routes/auth.js with below codeâ€”patches add full strategies for all platforms with token saves to user.tokens for posting/revokes, scopes/permissions per researched requirements to avoid invalid code/domain errors, no assumptionsâ€”extends your new version's FB focus to LinkedIn/X/YouTube/Instagram via FB for complete connects/max posting value)
